          </div>
        </div><br><br>
        <span class="spacing"><b>- </b>Corn starch mix thickens while drying. You can mould it with your hands.</span><br>
               <div class="slideshow2">
          <div class="slide">
            <img src="a-4-1.jpg">
          </div>
          <div class="slide">
            <img src="a-4-2.jpg">
