          <div class="slide">
            <img src="a-4-3.jpg">
          </div>
            <div class="slide">
            <img src="a-4-4.jpg">
          </div>
        </div><br><br>
        <span class="spacing"><b>- </b>Once dried, the tapioca version can be softened again by soaking it in water. Then, drape it over your mould and let it dry.</span><br>
  
        <h2><span class="spacing">*Thin sheets dry faster – often within a day.</span></h2><br>

        <b>If it cracks, splits..</b><br>
          <span class="spacing"><b>01</b></span><span class="spacing"> Don’t panic!</span><br>
          <span class="spacing"><b>02</b></span><span class="spacing"> Enjoy its natural materiality</span><br>
        <span class="spacing"><b>03</b><span class="spacing"> Reinforce - let your pot grow with time</span><br></span>

        <span class="spacing"><b>- </b>Add more paste where needed.</span><br>
          <div class="slideshow3">
          <div class="slide">
            <img src="a-2-1.jpg">
          </div>
