            <img src="a-2-3.jpg">
          </div>
        </div><br><br>
        <span class="spacing"><b>- </b>Soak dry tapioca scraps in water. Once it gets soft, fill gaps and let dry again.</span><br>
                           <div class="slideshow4">
          <div class="slide">
