            <img src="a-3-3.jpg">
          </div>
        </div><br><br>
        <span class="spacing">*Thin layers dry faster. May take a day.</span><br><br>

        <b>Note..</b><br>
        <span class="spacing"><b>- </b>If starch bioplastic is soaked in water, it softens and may lose shape.</span><br>
        <span class="spacing"><b>- </b>Keep indoors.</span><br>
        <h2><span class="spacing">* Ideal for dry-loving plants like cactus.</span></h2>
